				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Quang-B%C3%ADch/D%E1%BA%A1-ch%C3%AD-l%C3%A2m-trung-v%C3%B4-nh%C3%A2n-gia-k%E1%BA%BFt-li%C3%AAu-vi-tr%C3%BA/poem-C55jLV5qtmcLFpkmwMUnzQ">Dạ chí lâm trung vô nhân gia kết liêu vi trú - 夜至林中無人家結寮爲住</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Quang-B%C3%ADch/author-8mt7NYTrWG0XGzG7oOwfaw">Nguyễn Quang Bích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Du-Ti%C3%AAn-L%E1%BB%AF-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-v%C4%83n-nh%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C3%A0m-Th%C3%A1i-Nguy%C3%AAn-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-chi-th%E1%BA%AFng-tu%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%ADu-th%C3%A0nh-ng%C3%A2m/poem-brX0JwY5PNTxSGgywPw-YQ">Du Tiên Lữ động văn nhân đàm Thái Nguyên sơn thuỷ chi thắng, tuý hậu thành ngâm - 遊仙侶洞聞人談太原山水之勝醉後成吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/%C4%90oan-ng%E1%BB%8D-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-f6bAKlVocDRUmChfZzOBPQ">Đoan ngọ nhật - 端午日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/H%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%C4%83ng-c%E1%BB%B1c/poem-vnlH5urVf16jfz50t4v5ag">Hạ đăng cực - 賀登極</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/H%C3%A0n-than-%C4%91%C3%A3i-phi%E1%BA%BFm-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-vu0tjwSQvoDVXz1RmWNmpg">Hàn than đãi phiếm kỳ 2 - 寒灘待泛其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ch%C3%A2u-ca-th%E1%BA%ADp-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-p72Ht7AAKpWfbP-8kTtzEg">Quỳ Châu ca thập tuyệt cú kỳ 1 - 夔州歌十絕句其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Thanh-H%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-k%C3%BD/poem-4T3tCDz0kElUt1cfxT71ww">Thanh Hư động ký - 清虛洞記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thi%C3%AAn-tr%C3%AC/poem-48cMVmrKt3K81xBMPNTdYw">Thiên trì - 天池</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Tu%E1%BA%A7n-th%E1%BB%8B-Ch%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C4%83ng-ch%C3%A2u/poem-A9d3W-TENBDMfeekikcTYQ">Tuần thị Chân Đăng châu - 巡視真登州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/%C6%AF-Huy%E1%BB%81n-V%C5%A9-pha-t%C3%A1c/poem-6j0eRkgz9qmB3I_cEHxVFw">Ư Huyền Vũ pha tác - 於玄武陂作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br></div>	</div>
